deck: A former professional basketball player who underwent Terrigenesis, gaining the ability to transfer his mind from different hosts and while doing so, retain their thoughts.
description:
Origin

Morris Sackett was a professional basketball player until the point when the Terrigen Mists transformed him into Mosaic and it was revealed that he was an Inhuman.

Creation

Mosaic was created by Geoffrey Thorne but first appeared in Uncanny Inhumans issue 11 (2016)

Major Story Arcs

Civil War II

Mosaic was recruited by Medusa because of his unique ability to transfer his consciousness from host to host. While doing so, he takes all their memories for however he is in use of their body. Medusa utilized this power and had Mosaic take the form of Iron Man's financial manager and transfer away all of his funds.

Bessie Hotchkiss is an employee at Andrew Jackson High School. The same school that T'Challa taught at under the guise of Luke Charles. The Vision disguised as a friend of Luke Charles alerted her that his friend had been detained and that he wouldn't be able to make it that day. The way that he spoke gave the elderly woman quite the shock.

Unbeknownst to Bessie the reason Luke Charles was unavailable was because he was being held by the Lethal Legion.

deck: An AI created by an unnamed dictator used to police and "protect" his people.
description:
This artificial intelligence housed on an island run by an unnamed dictator was used to police and repress the people who lived there. It wasn't until a group of rebels were able to escape and were found almost dead by Tony Stark were they able to obtain help by the hero known as Iron Man.

Iron Man went to the infiltrated the island and destroyed The Overseer and another robotic enemy named Myrmidon freeing the people from the tyranny of the machine and dictator. However the courage and forgiveness of the people made them look towards a brighter future over a vengeful one.
